2.  **ZAMACE Launches Input Loan Facility for Smallholder Farmers**
    The Zambia Commodities Exchange (ZAMACE) and NewGrowCo Zambia introduced a 100% loan repayment scheme for smallholder farmers in Lusaka, Chongwe, Mpongwe, and Mkushi, using the Warehouse Receipt System to transform harvested crops into collateral, directly supporting increased agricultural capacity and food security.

